## 5. Service (ClusterIP + headless for StatefulSets)

**ClusterIP (default):**

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: api-worker
  namespace: webex-persistence
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: api-worker
  ports:
    - name: http
      port: 80
      targetPort: http
```

**Headless (`None`) — stable DNS per pod:** `pod-name.service.namespace.svc.cluster.local`

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: kafka-broker-hl
  namespace: webex-persistence
spec:
  clusterIP: None
  selector:
    app: kafka-broker
  ports:
    - name: kafka
      port: 9092
      targetPort: 9092
```

