## 8. PersistentVolumeClaim (dynamic provisioning — EBS `gp3`)

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolumeClaim
metadata:
  name: app-data
  namespace: webex-persistence
spec:
  accessModes:
    - ReadWriteOnce
  storageClassName: gp3
  resources:
    requests:
      storage: 50Gi
```

