## 10. PodDisruptionBudget (availability during node drains / upgrades)

```yaml
apiVersion: policy/v1
kind: PodDisruptionBudget
metadata:
  name: api-worker-pdb
  namespace: webex-persistence
spec:
  minAvailable: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: api-worker
```

**Alternative:** `maxUnavailable: 1` for batch-style workloads.

