## 11. CronJob (scheduled tasks — backups, reports, partition reassign helper)

```yaml
apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: nightly-db-backup
  namespace: webex-persistence
spec:
  schedule: "0 2 * * *"
  concurrencyPolicy: Forbid
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 3
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 3
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
          containers:
            - name: backup
              image: postgres:16-alpine
              command: ["/bin/sh", "-c", "pg_dump -h $PGHOST -U $PGUSER $PGDATABASE | gzip -c > /tmp/dump.sql.gz"]
              envFrom:
                - secretRef:
                    name: app-db
```

