## 12. Job (one-off migration / reindex)

```yaml
apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: Job
metadata:
  name: schema-migrate-20250403
  namespace: webex-persistence
spec:
  backoffLimit: 2
  ttlSecondsAfterFinished: 86400
  template:
    spec:
      restartPolicy: Never
      containers:
        - name: migrate
          image: 123456789012.dkr.ecr.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/webex/migrate:v1.0.0
