## 15. DaemonSet (node-level agent — log forwarders, node-exporter)

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: DaemonSet
metadata:
  name: log-forwarder
  namespace: webex-persistence
spec:
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: log-forwarder
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: log-forwarder
    spec:
      tolerations:
        - operator: Exists
          effect: NoSchedule
      containers:
        - name: fluent-bit
          image: fluent/fluent-bit:3.0
          volumeMounts:
            - name: varlog
              mountPath: /var/log
              readOnly: true
      volumes:
        - name: varlog
          hostPath:
            path: /var/log
            type: Directory
```

