## Quick interview map (JD → manifest)

| JD theme | Manifests to mention |
|----------|----------------------|
| Kafka / streaming | `StatefulSet`, headless `Service`, `PDB`, storage, possibly Strimzi/operator (not shown—too long) |
| AWS | ECR image refs, ALB `Ingress` annotations, `gp3` / CSI, IRSA (`serviceAccount` + IAM role annotation), **Secrets Manager** (CSI `SecretProviderClass` or ESO `ExternalSecret`) |
| Postgres | `Deployment` or operator CR; `CronJob` backup; `Secret` + TLS |
| CI/CD (Jenkins/GitHub) | Build pushes image → same Deployment tag bump; GitOps (Argo/Flux) applies these YAMLs |
| Flask / SQLAlchemy / cache | `Deployment`, `Service`, `ConfigMap`, Redis as `Deployment`+`Service` or ElastiCache outside cluster |
| SRE / HA | `PDB`, `HPA`, probes, rolling strategy, multiple AZ via node affinity (below) |

